<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy – Warehouse Furniture Killeen, TX" %>
<% content_for :description, "Privacy Policy for Warehouse Furniture. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-950 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-warm-500 mb-10">Last updated: April 26, 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-warm max-w-none space-y-8 text-warm-800">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Warehouse Furniture ("we," "our," or "us") is a furniture retailer located at 1104 E Veterans Memorial Blvd, Killeen, TX 76541. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit our website or make a purchase.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name, email address, and password when you create an account.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Sign-In:</strong> If you sign in with Google, we receive your name and email address from Google. We do not receive your Google password.</li>
        <li><strong>Order information:</strong> Shipping address, phone number, and purchase details when you place an order.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment information:</strong> Payments are processed securely by Stripe. We never store your full card number.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited and actions taken on our site, used to improve your experience.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>To process and fulfill your orders</li>
        <li>To send order confirmations and delivery updates by email</li>
        <li>To maintain your account and order history</li>
        <li>To respond to your questions and support requests</li>
        <li>To improve our website and services</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share data only as necessary to operate our business:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — payment processing</li>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — transactional email delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Google</strong> — OAuth sign-in (only if you choose to sign in with Google)</li>
        <li>Delivery personnel employed by Warehouse Furniture, solely to complete your delivery</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your account and order information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. You may request deletion of your account at any time by contacting us.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use session cookies to keep you signed in and to maintain your shopping cart. We do not use third-party advertising cookies.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at the address below. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">8. Security</h2>
      <p>We use industry-standard security measures including HTTPS encryption and secure payment processing. No method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, but we take reasonable steps to protect your information.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes by posting the new policy on this page with an updated date.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
      <address class="not-italic mt-2 space-y-1">
        <p><strong>Warehouse Furniture</strong></p>
        <p>1104 E Veterans Memorial Blvd</p>
        <p>Killeen, TX 76541</p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+12546289088" class="text-warm-700 underline">(254) 628-9088</a></p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:sales@warehousefurnituretx.com" class="text-warm-700 underline">sales@warehousefurnituretx.com</a></p>
      </address>
    </section>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-warm-200">
    <%= link_to "← Back to Home", root_path, class: "text-sm text-warm-600 hover:text-warm-900 transition-colors" %>
    <span class="mx-3 text-warm-300">|</span>
    <%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_path, class: "text-sm text-warm-600 hover:text-warm-900 transition-colors" %>
  </div>
</div>
